Some are so cute and others are really funny!! and we learned a new saying, but I dunno if I should tell it... maybe later. 

But while I was gone my mom and dad fixed my bed that I broke b/c when I was moving it then bottom part that the box-spring and mattress sit on fell out b/c my bed is like an antique (which means its old!) so it's fragile. Now I'm going to be cleaning for like another week b/c all the stuff that was under my bed (I won't even begin to tell you all the stuff, b/c that would take like 2 years) has to be put into these container things and then put back under, so that will be my life until my brothers get back.

But orientation is going to be so long tomorrow!! gah! It's like 4 and 1/2 hours!! But everyone will be there so that will be cool! but yea! this is really long! so I think I'll end it!
